#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.groupby.GroupBy.rolling.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.groupby.GroupBy.rolling"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:1 of
msgid "Return a rolling grouper, providing rolling functionality per group."
msgstr "返回一个滚动分组器，为每个分组提供滚动功能。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:3 of
msgid ""
"Size of the moving window.  If an integer, the fixed number of "
"observations used for each window.  If a timedelta, str, or offset, the "
"time period of each window. Each window will be a variable sized based on"
" the observations included in the time-period. This is only valid for "
"datetimelike indexes. To learn more about the offsets & frequency "
"strings, please see `this link <https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-"
"docs/stable/user_guide/timeseries.html#offset-aliases>`__.  If a "
"BaseIndexer subclass, the window boundaries based on the defined "
"``get_window_bounds`` method. Additional rolling keyword arguments, "
"namely ``min_periods``, ``center``, ``closed`` and ``step`` will be "
"passed to ``get_window_bounds``."
msgstr ""
"移动窗口的大小。如果为整数，则为每个窗口使用的固定观测数量。如果为 "
"timedelta、str 或 offset，则为每个窗口的时间周期。每个窗口的大小将根据"
"时间周期内包含的观测值而变化。这仅对类似日期时间的索引有效。如需了解更多"
"关于偏移量和频率字符串的信息，请参见 `此链接 <https://pandas.pydata.org/"
"pandas-docs/stable/user_guide/timeseries.html#offset-aliases>`__。如果为 "
"BaseIndexer 子类，则窗口边界基于定义的 ``get_window_bounds`` 方法。其他"
"滚动关键字参数，如 ``min_periods``、``center``、``closed`` 和 ``step`` 将"
"传递给 ``get_window_bounds``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:3 of
msgid "Size of the moving window."
msgstr "移动窗口的大小。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:5 of
msgid "If an integer, the fixed number of observations used for each window."
msgstr "如果为整数，则为每个窗口使用的固定观测数量。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:8 of
msgid ""
"If a timedelta, str, or offset, the time period of each window. Each "
"window will be a variable sized based on the observations included in the"
" time-period. This is only valid for datetimelike indexes. To learn more "
"about the offsets & frequency strings, please see `this link "
"<https://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/user_guide/timeseries.html"
"#offset-aliases>`__."
msgstr ""
"如果为 timedelta、str 或 offset，则为每个窗口的时间周期。每个窗口的大小将"
"根据时间周期内包含的观测值而变化。这仅对类似日期时间的索引有效。如需了解"
"更多关于偏移量和频率字符串的信息，请参见 `此链接 <https://pandas.pydata."
"org/pandas-docs/stable/user_guide/timeseries.html#offset-aliases>`__。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:14 of
msgid ""
"If a BaseIndexer subclass, the window boundaries based on the defined "
"``get_window_bounds`` method. Additional rolling keyword arguments, "
"namely ``min_periods``, ``center``, ``closed`` and ``step`` will be "
"passed to ``get_window_bounds``."
msgstr ""
"如果为 BaseIndexer 子类，则窗口边界基于定义的 ``get_window_bounds`` 方法"
"。其他滚动关键字参数，如 ``min_periods``、``center``、``closed`` 和 ``"
"step`` 将传递给 ``get_window_bounds``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:19 of
msgid ""
"Minimum number of observations in window required to have a value; "
"otherwise, result is ``np.nan``.  For a window that is specified by an "
"offset, ``min_periods`` will default to 1.  For a window that is "
"specified by an integer, ``min_periods`` will default to the size of the "
"window."
msgstr ""
"窗口中需要包含的最小观测数以产生值；否则结果为 ``np.nan``。对于由偏移量"
"指定的窗口，``min_periods`` 默认为 1。对于由整数指定的窗口，``min_periods"
"`` 默认为窗口的大小。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:19 of
msgid ""
"Minimum number of observations in window required to have a value; "
"otherwise, result is ``np.nan``."
msgstr "窗口中需要包含的最小观测数以产生值；否则结果为 ``np.nan``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:22 of
msgid ""
"For a window that is specified by an offset, ``min_periods`` will default"
" to 1."
msgstr "对于由偏移量指定的窗口，``min_periods`` 默认为 1。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:25 of
msgid ""
"For a window that is specified by an integer, ``min_periods`` will "
"default to the size of the window."
msgstr "对于由整数指定的窗口，``min_periods`` 默认为窗口的大小。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:28 of
msgid ""
"If False, set the window labels as the right edge of the window index.  "
"If True, set the window labels as the center of the window index."
msgstr ""
"如果为 False，则将窗口标签设置为窗口索引的右边缘。如果为 True，则将窗口"
"标签设置为窗口索引的中心。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:28 of
msgid "If False, set the window labels as the right edge of the window index."
msgstr "如果为 False，则将窗口标签设置为窗口索引的右边缘。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:30 of
msgid "If True, set the window labels as the center of the window index."
msgstr "如果为 True，则将窗口标签设置为窗口索引的中心。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:32 of
msgid ""
"If ``None``, all points are evenly weighted.  If a string, it must be a "
"valid `scipy.signal window function "
"<https://docs.scipy.org/doc/scipy/reference/signal.windows.html#module-"
"scipy.signal.windows>`__.  Certain Scipy window types require additional "
"parameters to be passed in the aggregation function. The additional "
"parameters must match the keywords specified in the Scipy window type "
"method signature."
msgstr ""
"如果为 ``None``，则所有点的权重相等。如果为字符串，则必须是有效的 `scipy."
"signal 窗口函数 <https://docs.scipy.org/doc/scipy/reference/signal."
"windows.html#module-scipy.signal.windows>`__。某些 Scipy 窗口类型在聚合"
"函数中需要传递额外参数。这些额外参数必须匹配 Scipy 窗口类型方法签名中指定"
"的关键字。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:32 of
msgid "If ``None``, all points are evenly weighted."
msgstr "如果为 ``None``，则所有点的权重相等。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:34 of
msgid ""
"If a string, it must be a valid `scipy.signal window function "
"<https://docs.scipy.org/doc/scipy/reference/signal.windows.html#module-"
"scipy.signal.windows>`__."
msgstr ""
"如果为字符串，则必须是有效的 `scipy.signal 窗口函数 <https://docs.scipy."
"org/doc/scipy/reference/signal.windows.html#module-scipy.signal.windows>`"
"__。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:37 of
msgid ""
"Certain Scipy window types require additional parameters to be passed in "
"the aggregation function. The additional parameters must match the "
"keywords specified in the Scipy window type method signature."
msgstr ""
"某些 Scipy 窗口类型在聚合函数中需要传递额外参数。这些额外参数必须匹配 "
"Scipy 窗口类型方法签名中指定的关键字。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:41 of
msgid ""
"For a DataFrame, a column label or Index level on which to calculate the "
"rolling window, rather than the DataFrame's index.  Provided integer "
"column is ignored and excluded from result since an integer index is not "
"used to calculate the rolling window."
msgstr ""
"对于 DataFrame，指定用于计算滚动窗口的列标签或索引级别，而不是 DataFrame "
"的索引。由于整数索引不用于计算滚动窗口，提供的整数列将被忽略并从结果中"
"排除。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:41 of
msgid ""
"For a DataFrame, a column label or Index level on which to calculate the "
"rolling window, rather than the DataFrame's index."
msgstr ""
"对于 DataFrame，指定用于计算滚动窗口的列标签或索引级别，而不是 DataFrame "
"的索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:44 of
msgid ""
"Provided integer column is ignored and excluded from result since an "
"integer index is not used to calculate the rolling window."
msgstr "由于整数索引不用于计算滚动窗口，提供的整数列将被忽略并从结果中排除。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:47 of
msgid ""
"If ``0`` or ``'index'``, roll across the rows.  If ``1`` or "
"``'columns'``, roll across the columns.  For `Series` this parameter is "
"unused and defaults to 0."
msgstr ""
"如果为 ``0`` 或 ``'index'``，则在行上滚动。如果为 ``1`` 或 ``'columns'``"
"，则在列上滚动。对于 `Series`，此参数未使用，默认为 0。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:47 of
msgid "If ``0`` or ``'index'``, roll across the rows."
msgstr "如果为 ``0`` 或 ``'index'``，则在行上滚动。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:49 of
msgid "If ``1`` or ``'columns'``, roll across the columns."
msgstr "如果为 ``1`` 或 ``'columns'``，则在列上滚动。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:51 of
msgid "For `Series` this parameter is unused and defaults to 0."
msgstr "对于 `Series`，此参数未使用，默认为 0。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:53 of
msgid ""
"If ``'right'``, the first point in the window is excluded from "
"calculations.  If ``'left'``, the last point in the window is excluded "
"from calculations.  If ``'both'``, no points in the window are excluded "
"from calculations.  If ``'neither'``, the first and last points in the "
"window are excluded from calculations.  Default ``None`` (``'right'``)."
msgstr ""
"如果为 ``'right'``，则窗口中的第一个点不参与计算。如果为 ``'left'``，则"
"窗口中的最后一个点不参与计算。如果为 ``'both'``，则窗口中的所有点都参与"
"计算。如果为 ``'neither'``，则窗口中的第一个和最后一个点都不参与计算。"
"默认为 ``None``（即 ``'right'``）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:53 of
msgid ""
"If ``'right'``, the first point in the window is excluded from "
"calculations."
msgstr "如果为 ``'right'``，则窗口中的第一个点不参与计算。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:55 of
msgid "If ``'left'``, the last point in the window is excluded from calculations."
msgstr "如果为 ``'left'``，则窗口中的最后一个点不参与计算。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:57 of
msgid "If ``'both'``, no points in the window are excluded from calculations."
msgstr "如果为 ``'both'``，则窗口中的所有点都参与计算。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:59 of
msgid ""
"If ``'neither'``, the first and last points in the window are excluded "
"from calculations."
msgstr "如果为 ``'neither'``，则窗口中的第一个和最后一个点都不参与计算。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:62 of
msgid "Default ``None`` (``'right'``)."
msgstr "默认为 ``None``（即 ``'right'``）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.rolling.rolling:64 of
msgid ""
"If specified, the window will be shifted by `shift` rows (or data will be"
" shifted by `-shift` rows) before computing window function."
msgstr ""
"如果指定，则在计算窗口函数之前，窗口将按 `shift` 行进行偏移（或者数据将按"
" `-shift` 行进行偏移）。"

